{"tid":1506192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好比個背脊比我地既敵人","createTime":"2019-08-25T17:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T18:52:06.000Z","uid":238768,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf2e8659a607ad1f0cfd35501ac2757dd59bae0","tid":1506192,"uid":238768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:37:14.000Z","msg":"少少睇法<br />\n水炮車出左第一次 一定會有下一次<br />\n棍 椒 tg 子彈 甚至堅實彈<br />\n無一個黑警係無辜 佢地咩都做得出<br />\n有不反對書同無不反對書結果都會係一樣<br />\n請各位出去發夢 遊行 集會 落街食糖水 都要記得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好落單</span><br />\n<br />\n前線手足 824觀塘同今日荃灣都係一個問題<br />\n我地比左個最脆弱既背脊比敵人呀<br />\n背住佢 佢跑得幾快 幾多人 出子彈 拉手足<br />\n都唔會知道 更加救唔到人<br />\n我知救人手足都被捕而且唔止一個<br />\nFight or Flight係一個好大既關卡 正常人都會驚<br />\n我建議 facing對住狗 慢退或急退 手拉住手足背囊（出動手炮車除外 水炮車威力十分大不可忽視）<br />\n而且<br />\n戰線回復612 頭4-5排後有一大段空位比前線夠距離跑<br />\n824觀塘完全無位比人跑堆哂一舊 前線同狗距離唔夠100米 到最後拉左幾多手足？<br />\n勇武手足拉少見少 佢地永遠企第一排幫我地擋槍口 走既時候永遠最後一排<br />\n唔比翻咁上下距離真係走唔切架 連續兩日都係咁呀大家<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">企疏啲 唔好咁密集</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今日被捕手足好多 我唔敢行到最前 但我幫人急救既時候都不斷喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S <strong>特別係無咩力既巴絲 衡量過距離根本唔夠既話唔好擲竹擲磚 今日幫左兩個前線止血個頭同手都忽磚頭打到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />忽自己人整傷好無奈 之前新城市戰場已經試過好多次 真係請大家留意 </strong>"},{"pid":"3b2258cefd2623d35cda54fff529d7104a1613c3","tid":1506192,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:37:52.000Z","msg":"借po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小心個袋俾狗咬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1506145/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1506145/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c1839462f074bef16153218a719b83980c04c61b","tid":1506192,"uid":238768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"f9f773450a022312b14daf8b02c0331c719467c4","tid":1506192,"uid":238768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:41:20.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"5aa941117265a9200d072656773b473c3f17a8f3","tid":1506192,"uid":238768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:41:30.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"f1934b441f097069237a95cd99d8e01f7040d2a4","tid":1506192,"uid":238768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:41:40.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"848e4cddd1726e3dd5f3f7f6c7747e6a77605c82","tid":1506192,"uid":238768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:41:52.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"c01abd5906fced589113d830c3d1e76203905a08","tid":1506192,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:03.000Z","msg":"企疏啲<br />\n慢慢退<br />\n停<br />\n衝<br />\n救人"},{"pid":"9339af889474250d5c84d76aeedf43246ec3a76e","tid":1506192,"uid":238768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:04.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"d873b0c1efd49a7777208e295d8c35da9b9f48f4","tid":1506192,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:09.000Z","msg":"［緊急！］反對曾偉雄既白宮聯署有問題！多人表示收唔到確認email!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503718</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n個petition已經24個小時冇郁過個人數！！！<br />\n懷疑中共做左手腳"},{"pid":"b2286e0b7cf8dd6c074de9a0915ad779cfa0aacf","tid":1506192,"uid":238768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:20.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"257e5a4a1b09794bb7bde7a7a967c43c7481e68e","tid":1506192,"uid":238768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:53.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c06be9899a96e01217d9a0d11959a56dc7285cfc","tid":1506192,"uid":141039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:43:02.000Z","msg":"慢慢走, 唔好急"},{"pid":"b2e